He's Zou Mian's son-in-law,

23
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:47,630
Luan Hui.

24
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:53,120
He's the role model for men who want to marry above

25
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,040
their stations.

26
00:01:59,770 --> 00:02:02,400
The clues to the murder in the Fan Building led us directly here.

27
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,310
We are only following orders.

28
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,360
Following orders?

29
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,720
Whose orders?

30
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:17,130
You clueless peasant.

31
00:02:18,550 --> 00:02:19,190
Get lost.

32
00:02:23,470 --> 00:02:24,960
How dare you!

33
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,720
Show some manners.

34
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:30,960
They are our distinguished guests.

35
00:02:34,270 --> 00:02:37,470
What an ignorant clown.

36
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:40,190
Drop it.

37
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:46,600
Inspector Gu.

38
00:02:46,970 --> 00:02:48,240
Inspector Gu.

39
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,800
Please come in.

40
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,280
Lower your sword now.

41
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:30,830
Such powerful strokes.

42
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:33,370
What a delicate brushwork.

43
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,520
So unrestrained.

44
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,880
What a unique style.

45
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,880
You must

46
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:39,270
write something

47
00:03:39,270 --> 00:03:41,190
for my Yayuan Mansion one day.

48
00:03:48,830 --> 00:03:49,960
Who is Luan Hui?

49
00:03:54,780 --> 00:03:56,780
[Luan Hui, Son-in-law of Zou Mian]

50
00:03:58,110 --> 00:03:59,030
So you're Luan Hui?

51
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,630
I am the Zuojun Inspector of Kaifeng Court.

52
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,630
My name is Gu Zhen.

53
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,550
A murder

54
00:04:03,550 --> 00:04:05,390
occurred outside the Donghua Gate today.

55
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:06,670
The evidence obtained

56
00:04:06,670 --> 00:04:07,720
at the scene led us here.

57
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,720
I need to search the Yayuan Mansion.

58
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,080
Please cooperate.

59
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:14,190
What a clown.

60
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,440
How dare you disturb me

61
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:19,110
and my friends while we're having fun.

62
00:04:20,230 --> 00:04:21,230
Who's the clown here?

63
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,670
Me.

64
00:04:23,110 --> 00:04:24,040
I'm the clown.

65
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,040
Mr. Luan.

66
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,760
Inspector Gu

67
00:04:26,790 --> 00:04:28,440
