68
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,670
I couldn't stop him.

69
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:30,540
Nonsense!

70
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:31,210
You let us in!

71
00:04:31,210 --> 00:04:32,180
Useless!

72
00:04:33,770 --> 00:04:35,040
Please forgive me, Mr. Luan.

73
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,790
Kaifeng Court?

74
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,510
Just a second.

75
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:50,880
Well...

76
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,640
What does

77
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,320
the Kaifeng Court want from me?

78
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:57,860
[Governor of Kaifeng Court]

79
00:05:01,110 --> 00:05:01,830
Governor.

80
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:04,480
What happened?

81
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:06,790
What's the fuss about?

82
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,670
Governor.

83
00:05:09,230 --> 00:05:09,830
Earlier today,

84
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:12,070
a murder occurred at the Fan Building

85
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:13,110
outside the Donghua Gate.

86
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:15,010
Someone dumped the bodies in public.

87
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:16,790
The victims were three males.

88
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:19,160
A fish charm was found in the throat

89
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,480
of one of the corpses.

90
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,320
Three fish charms.

91
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:25,160
Each body had one.

92
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,880
Investigation shows

93
00:05:35,790 --> 00:05:36,600
that those fish charms

94
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,040
are the passes to the Yayuan Mansion.

95
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,040
I suspect

96
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,950
that someone is trying to frame

97
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,200
Mr. Luan.

98
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,510
Therefore,

99
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:49,950
I came to inquire about this

100
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:52,200
with Mr. Luan.

101
00:05:52,790 --> 00:05:53,550
I wonder

102
00:05:54,110 --> 00:05:55,950
if Mr. Luan has any enemies.

103
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:59,510
Or have you offended someone recently?

104
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,920
Sorry about that.

105
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,670
You said you were

106
00:06:17,350 --> 00:06:18,550
Inspector Gu.

107
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,200
Gu Zhen.

108
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:24,160
I think you have a point.

109
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,920
Someone must have set me up.

110
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:30,040
Everyone here knows my Yayuan Mansion.

111
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:33,230
How could it possibly harbor filth and evil?

112
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:37,920
I only socialize with well-educated men.

113
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,550
The governor

114
00:06:39,550 --> 00:06:41,830
and all these scholars can testify for me.

115
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:44,600
The fish charm.

116
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:50,160
There's nothing

117
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:52,480
special about this fish charm.

118
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,390
How can you tell that's from my Yayuan Mansion?

119
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,670
Besides,

120
00:06:56,670 --> 00:06:59,160
you haven't even figured out how many fish charms there are

121
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,930
and are here to search my mansion.

122
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,110
Isn't it a bit too abrupt,

123
00:07:03,110 --> 00:07:04,440
Inspector Gu?

124
00:07:07,110 --> 00:07:09,760
I am generally on good terms with people

125
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,230
and often make friends.

126
00:07:11,550 --> 00:07:13,790
I have no personal enmity with anyone.

127
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,200
I can't think of an enemy

128
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,790
even if you ask me to.

129
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,070
However,

130
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,160
it's fine.

131
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:21,160
Since you insist on inspecting my mansion...

132
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,880
Steward.

133
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,040
Tell everyone to open the doors to each room.

134
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,950
Let Inspector Gu conduct a thorough investigation

135
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:30,720
so that I can prove my innocence.

136
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,720
Wait.

137
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,610
It is too hasty

138
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:38,320
to conclude that the case is related to the Yayuan Mansion

139
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,800
with this item alone.

140
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,040
Governor.

141
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,550
Let's continue.

142
00:08:25,550 --> 00:08:26,200
After you.

143
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,110
Unbelievable.

144
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:34,610
Throw them away. Get new ones.

145
00:08:34,610 --> 00:08:41,220
[Yayuan Mansion]

146
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:48,520
Take care, gentlemen.

147
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:54,470
Boss.

148
00:08:55,230 --> 00:08:56,550
I've told you.

149
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,150
There are really

150
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,230
three fish charms.

151
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:07,670
Lady Wang.

152
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:09,960
Mr. Liu.

153
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,110
