156
00:09:13,850 --> 00:09:14,840
Nonsense!

157
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,150
The governor is right here.

158
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,620
I saw him just now.

159
00:09:20,350 --> 00:09:21,110
Lady Wang.

160
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,000
Your father

161
00:09:23,230 --> 00:09:24,350
is right inside.

162
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:26,180
Lady Wang.

163
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,450
Thank you.

164
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:29,000
Wait.

165
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,280
Lady Wang.

166
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:31,230
Get her.

167
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:32,760
Seriously, he's not here.

168
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,590
My master has business to do today.

169
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,150
Boss.

170
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:39,590
There are three fish charms.

171
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,050
Not bad.

172
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:57,910
Have you tried the pears from in there?

173
00:09:58,470 --> 00:09:59,280
No.

174
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:03,910
Not bad.

175
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:06,320
Here.

176
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:12,780
[Yayuan Mansion]

177
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:23,320
This is an important case.

178
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,760
Inspector Gu really needs your help.

179
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,910
We're counting on you.

180
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:31,470
Buyou.

181
00:10:31,470 --> 00:10:32,350
Wen Yue.

182
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:34,760
Zhao Ban.

183
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:36,470
- Why are you here? - Why are you here?

184
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:38,640
Well...

185
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:39,890
I came with Father

186
00:10:39,890 --> 00:10:41,000
