190
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,960
Our father?

191
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:54,080
I'm here.

192
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:55,880
Father.

193
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:56,880
He's there.

194
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,200
