195
00:10:58,760 --> 00:10:59,550
Mr. Zhao, be careful.

196
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,080
- Father. - Be careful.

197
00:11:02,590 --> 00:11:03,590
- Be careful. - Be careful.

