217
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,710
How complicated can it be?

218
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,280
Yayuan Mansion.

219
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:38,320
Isn't that

220
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,790
Luan Hui's place?

221
00:11:40,150 --> 00:11:41,320
