222
00:11:41,470 --> 00:11:42,670
He's just

223
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:45,080
the son-in-law of Mr. Zou.

224
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:48,840
In fact,

225
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,200
