234
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:11,230
and stop them from cheating.

235
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,960
Aren't these cases you're working on

236
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:18,150
all related to the Zou family?

237
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:19,440
Father.

238
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,470
How come you know everything?

239
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,230
There are too many plays

240
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:26,000
