241
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:28,030
Some are true.

242
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,880
Some are false.

243
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,550
What stories are true?

244
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:34,790
What stories are false?

245
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,000
Father.

246
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:37,590
That's enough.

247
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:39,000
The Kaifeng Court

248
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:41,350
