249
00:12:42,110 --> 00:12:42,880
Zhao Ban.

250
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,760
Take Father home.

251
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:44,470
Hurry up.

252
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:46,220
I want to stay and investigate.

253
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,020
Ban.

254
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:48,230
Go home.

255
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,520
I'll find you

256
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:50,470
